main_body:
Decision 2004/4/EC is amended as follows:
1. in Article 2 paragraph 1 ‘2006/07’ is replaced by ‘2007/08’;
2. in Article 4, ‘31 August 2007’ is replaced by ‘31 August 2008’;
3. in Article 7, ‘30 September 2007’ is replaced by ‘30 September 2008’;
4. the Annex is amended as follows:
(a) in point 1(b)(iii), ‘2006/07’ is replaced by ‘2007/08’;
(b) in the second indent of point 1(b)(iii), ‘1 January 2007’ is replaced by ‘1 January 2008’;
(c) in point 1(b)(xii), ‘1 January 2007’ is replaced by ‘1 January 2008’.
